<h2>Who is the Combo Tour For?</h2>
<p>The Starfish Sandbar + Little Boracay combo is ideal for:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Families with children</strong> — shallow, safe water at both stops; starfish are a highlight for kids</li>
  <li><strong>First-time visitors to Calatagan</strong> — see the best of both natural sandbars in one day</li>
  <li><strong>Photographers and drone operators</strong> — two visually stunning locations</li>
  <li><strong>Groups wanting a full-day experience</strong> — not just a single stop</li>
